doc: Identifies how the user can interact with a particular cell.

members.doc: The cell is just for display and cannot be interacted with. Note that this doesn’t mean that eg. the row being drawn can’t be selected -- just that a particular element of it cannot be individually modified.
members.name: inert

members.doc: The cell can be edited or otherwise modified.
members.name: editable

name: CellRendererMode
